Class LoggingCompletableSubscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.servicetalk.concurrent.api.LoggingCompletableSubscriber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompletableSource.Subscriber

    public class LoggingCompletableSubscriber
extends java.lang.Object
implements CompletableSource.Subscriber
    A CompletableSource.Subscriber that wraps another CompletableSource.Subscriber, logging all signals received by the CompletableSource.Subscriber, or sent via the Cancellable.
